data.description: Introducing Your Dream Ranch Home! Discover the perfect blend of comfort & elegance in this stunning ranch-style home. With cathedral ceilings that create an open & spacious atmosphere, this residence is a true gem. The heart of this home is the open kitchen, complete w a center island and  a charming breakfast nook. The main floor laundry room is conveniently located for ease of use, while the great room boasts a cozy gas fireplace, creating a warm and inviting space. Plus, it offers a captivating view of the backyard, so you can relax by the fire while taking in the scenic beauty. Your main floor master bedroom is a sanctuary, featuring a large private bath with a separate shower. And that's not all! This home also offers a screened-in porch for those days when you want to enjoy the outdoors without any pests to worry about.The basement is partially finished, and it includes a finished bathroom. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours! Buyer to verify all information.
